feature.name: Inter-RAT Offload to WCDMA
feature.summary: This feature performs handovers of LTE cell traffic to WCDMA FDD

parameters.description: See MOM description.

parameters.description: See MOM description.

parameters.description: See MOM description.

parameters.description: See MOM description.

parameters.description: See MOM description.

parameters.description: See MOM description.

parameters.name: UtranCellRelation.loadBalancing
parameters.description: See MOM description.

parameters.name: INTERNAL_EVENT_LB_INTER_FREQ
parameters.description: CGI of target cell participating in load balancing, if available.

parameters.name: INTERNAL_EVENT_LB_INTER_FREQ
parameters.description: Load difference in subscription ratio between source and neighbor cells.

parameters.name: INTERNAL_EVENT_LB_INTER_FREQ
parameters.description: Unsigned integer value of EVENT_PARAM_LB_DIFF; positive or                   negative.

parameters.name: INTERNAL_EVENT_LB_INTER_FREQ
parameters.description: Load balancing amount in subscription quanta to be moved from source to target                   cell.

parameters.name: INTERNAL_EVENT_LB_INTER_FREQ
parameters.description: Subscription ratio of source cell.

parameters.name: INTERNAL_EVENT_LB_INTER_FREQ
parameters.description: Subscription ratio of target cell.

parameters.name: INTERNAL_EVENT_LB_INTER_FREQ
parameters.description: Rate offset applied to offset the load balancing towards a cell with higher                   capacity, if the general traffic load level is low.

parameters.name: INTERNAL_EVENT_LB_INTER_FREQ
parameters.description: Unsigned integer value of EVENT_PARAM_LB_RATE_OFFSET; positive                   or negative.

parameters.name: INTERNAL_EVENT_UE_LB_MEAS
parameters.description: Target frequency.

parameters.name: INTERNAL_EVENT_UE_LB_MEAS
parameters.description: Indicates the function that has triggered the UE measurement and consequently the                   measurement report:    Load Balancing     CA triggered redirection     BNR for load balancing     ATO

parameters.name: INTERNAL_EVENT_UE_LB_MEAS
parameters.description: Indicates whether the UE selected for load balancing related measurements is CA                   capable.

parameters.name: INTERNAL_EVENT_UE_LB_MEAS
parameters.description: CGI of neighbor target cells for which the UE fulfilled the criteria for event                   A5.

parameters.name: INTERNAL_EVENT_UE_LB_MEAS
parameters.description: Number of UEs checked and discarded before choosing this UE for load balancing                   related measurements.

parameters.name: INTERNAL_EVENT_UE_LB_QUAL
parameters.description: CGI of neighbor target cells for which UE fulfilled A5 measurement criteria.

parameters.name: INTERNAL_EVENT_UE_LB_QUAL
parameters.description: Indicates the RAT of the source cell for incoming handover, or target cell for                   outgoing handover.

parameters.name: INTERNAL_EVENT_UE_LB_QUAL
parameters.description: Indicates the reason for not proceeding with a Load Balancing or CA triggered                   redirection action when a measurement report has been received from the UE:    CA criteria not met     Reported cell is not a valid load balancing target      Reported cell is a valid target, but lbAmount has already been satisfied for                       the cell     Service Specific Load Management related restrictions     RSRQ of target cell is below configured threshold     UE has signaled interest in MBMS service on serving frequency     UE has an ongoing VoIP call and does not support SRVCC     ATO related restrictions

parameters.name: INTERNAL_EVENT_UE_LB_QUAL
parameters.description: Indicates the function that has triggered the UE measurement and consequently the                   measurement report:    Load balancing     CA triggered redirection      BNR for load balancing     ATO

parameters.name: INTERNAL_PROC_HO_PREP_S1_OUT
parameters.description: The cause of the procedure for Handover Preparation:    CS     CA     SPIFHO     ATO

parameters.name: INTERNAL_EVENT_ONGOING_UE_MEAS
parameters.description: RSRP of the neighbor cell.

parameters.name: INTERNAL_EVENT_ONGOING_UE_MEAS
parameters.description: RSRQ of the neighbor cell.

parameters.name: INTERNAL_EVENT_UE_MEAS_FAILURE
parameters.description: The cause why the request to start UE Measurements was rejected.

parameters.name: INTERNAL_UE_MEAS_ABORT
parameters.description: The cause for the measurement in the UE being aborted.

parameters.name: INTERNAL_PROC_HO_EXEC_S1_OUT
parameters.description: The cause of the procedure for HO Execution.     CS     CA     SPIFHO     ATO

parameters.name: INTERNAL_EVENT_UE_MOBILITY_EVAL
parameters.description: Indicates the trigger for performing a mobility evaluation.    CS     CA     SPIFHO     ATO

parameters.name: INTERNAL_EVENT_MEAS_CONFIG_B1_UTRA
parameters.description: The UTRA threshold for RSCP. See 3GPP TS 36.331.

parameters.name: INTERNAL_EVENT_MEAS_CONFIG_B1_UTRA
parameters.description: Indicates the function that requested the UE measurement.

parameters.name: INTERNAL_EVENT_MEAS_CONFIG_B1_UTRA
parameters.description: Indicates the ARFCN value applicable for a downlink UTRA carrier frequency.
